snippet: The U.S. Air Force said it will resume flights of Lockheed Martin Corp's F-35 A-model fighter jets at a Florida air base on Wednesday, two days after one of the jets caught fire while preparing for takeoff....

headline.print_headline: U.S. Air Force to Resume F-35A Fighter Jet Flights Wednesday
headline.main: U.S. Air Force to Resume F-35A Fighter Jet Flights Wednesday

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Air Force said it will resume flights of Lockheed Martin Corp's F-35 A-model fighter jets at a Florida air base on Wednesday, two days after one of the jets caught fire while preparing for takeoff.
